parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities. It can also lead to loss of control, property damage, and emotional distress.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates without warning
often without the driver's input. This can occur while braking
shifting gears
or cruising. The acceleration may be sudden and rapid
making it difficult for the driver to regain control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the braking system and unintended acceleration can lead to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal does not respond
the vehicle accelerates unexpectedly
the vehicle fails to stop
the engine revs
and the anti-lock brakes grab and release.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The close proximity of the brake and accelerator pedals can lead to unintended acceleration and brake failure, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake and accelerator pedals are too close together
the pedals can be adjusted up and down but the problem persists
and the driver's foot can easily slip from the brake to the accelerator pedal.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Inadequate Diagnostic and Repair by Dealerships
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of dealerships to diagnose and repair the issues can lead to continued risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Dealerships are unable to duplicate the problem
no error codes are found in the computer system
and the problem is not addressed or repaired.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag warning light flashes
the airbag warning light remains on
the airbag system fails to deploy in an accident
the seat belt tensioners fail
the passenger side airbag fails
the driver side airbag fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt tensioners can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the seat belt tensioners fail
the passenger side seat belt tensioner fails
the driver side seat belt tensioner fails
the airbag system fails to deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clock spring can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the clock spring fails
the airbag system fails to deploy in an accident.
